descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i1234.photobucket.com/albums/ff411/nuclearlion73/dESCRIPTION.png[/IMG]
    This mod replaces Skyrim\'s dull boring moon with a new, exciting moon of your choice!

[IMG]http://i1234.photobucket.com/albums/ff411/nuclearlion73/other.png[/IMG]
  If you hate the mod, please let me know what I\'ve done wrong, and what I can do to improve my mod.

  If you love the mod, please let me know what you love about it so I can get a better taste of what people of the Nexus enjoy in their mods, also if you love it; please endorse it!

  If your complaint is that it\'s un-lore-friendly, please do keep the comment to yourself. Skyrim is a game based on fiction, this mod is a mod that adds on to the fiction.

Don\'t like it?
Don\'t download it,
Don\'t endorse it,
Don\'t flame it. 

[IMG]http://i1234.photobucket.com/albums/ff411/nuclearlion73/TODO.png[/IMG]
Planet X(Nibiru)
Earth
Uranus(lol)
Pluto
New Moon
Endor
Gliese 581
Titan
Ganymede
Callisto
Mercury
Triton
Io
Europa
Also open to suggestions.


[IMG]http://i1234.photobucket.com/albums/ff411/nuclearlion73/tHANKS.png[/IMG]
Bethesda - For the ability to mod Skyrim
Paint.net - For .DDS Support
Photoshop -  For the tools to create textures
